{"tid":1245830,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《戰爭機器5》將於2019年9月10登陸Xbox One和Steam平台，登陸PS4機會不大","createTime":"2019-06-20T12:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T05:25:03.000Z","uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b2c4de20a7154749a0d1cd7ffa5c4dffebb85ed6","tid":1245830,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:51:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2362807947323046\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2362807947323046&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=12c45fef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2362807947323046</a><br />\n<br />\nXbox總監談：是否會讓《戰爭機器5》登陸PS4<br />\n---<br />\n📣在微軟宣布與索尼進行雲遊戲合作之後，以及和任天堂和合作之後，關於微軟要轉向第三方的傳聞愈演愈烈。近日，在接受外媒Kotaku的採訪時，Xbox總監菲爾&middot;斯賓塞就被問到了是否會讓《戰爭機器5》登陸PS4這樣的問題。<br />\n<br />\n外媒Kotaku記者Totilo問：如果微軟有辦法的話，會不會讓《戰爭機器5》在9月份登陸PS4平台？<br />\n<br />\nXbox總監菲爾&middot;斯賓塞：我覺得Xbox給大家的客廳帶來的新體驗是專注於向下兼容和跨平台的，這也未來Xbox遊戲發展的重要目標，這也是為什麼我們花費大量的資金和資源去打造新主機Xbox Scarlett，PC端也是一樣。所以，現在就有人說了，微軟是不是要走第三方之路？不管這些人說這個話是什麼意思，微軟還是​​會走獨立平台道路。我們也考慮過一個遊戲平台的基礎設施應該如何發展，那就是在家裡放一台世界上最牛最強的Xbox，這就是實現我們未來計劃最關鍵的部分。<br />\n<br />\n當然，Xbox總監菲爾&middot;斯賓塞並沒有在採訪中直接說&ldquo;不可能&rdquo;，可是他明確地表示了&ldquo;微軟還是會走獨立平台道路&rdquo;，這也意味著目前《戰爭機器5》還會是微軟第一方獨占大作，可在後面的採訪中菲爾則談到了&ldquo;讓玩家們在遊戲整個生態圈中分享自己的成就、交友以及使用遊戲存檔是很重要的，而且目前Xbox上還沒有這樣的生態鏈。&rdquo;也許這句話的意思是，在這種功能出現之前，微軟的第一方遊戲還會是獨占。<br />\n<br />\n微軟第一方大作《戰爭機器5》將於2019年9月10登陸Xbox One和Steam平台。<br />\n------<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5oD3tLD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5oD3tLD.jpg&h=bb76291e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LHjqG5D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLHjqG5D.png&h=ec3fc4d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fvQ9piZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfvQ9piZ.jpg&h=0d26ed8d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"926832f2b75f86fe8cc667ccf72a7723fa9c47a5","tid":1245830,"uid":8902,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:33:07.000Z","msg":"邊有可能上ps4，問果個係咪傻架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d098e3b689e23fbae0b41b47b02a0e2029afe9","tid":1245830,"uid":9104,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:38:03.000Z","msg":"Halo幾時上ps4"},{"pid":"745b9ef098888a5af0f424fe60b45000e88a943a","tid":1245830,"uid":40763,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:38:57.000Z","msg":"呢隻垃圾仲死唔斷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9ab37f11e823708739782fa3e1300bec6200fd","tid":1245830,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8d098e3b689e23fbae0b41b47b02a0e2029afe9","tid":1245830,"uid":9104,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:38:03.000Z","msg":"Halo幾時上ps4"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:39:12.000Z","msg":"mario去ps4"},{"pid":"fb56d68bd3f146002ef5203a9fef00ebdd41c90d","tid":1245830,"uid":236891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"745b9ef098888a5af0f424fe60b45000e88a943a","tid":1245830,"uid":40763,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:38:57.000Z","msg":"呢隻垃圾仲死唔斷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:39:38.000Z","msg":"好心3好完鬼咗佢"},{"pid":"292b968af4464cd8419f3fb0a38f479feff5ef8d","tid":1245830,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb56d68bd3f146002ef5203a9fef00ebdd41c90d","tid":1245830,"uid":236891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"745b9ef098888a5af0f424fe60b45000e88a943a","tid":1245830,"uid":40763,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:38:57.000Z","msg":"呢隻垃圾仲死唔斷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:39